Distribution.
Gopkittisak gallardoi
was originally described from Andaman Sea, Thailand (
Serène & Soh, 1976
). They also recoded it from Nhatrang Bay, Vietnam . Subsequently the species has been recorded from Pakistan (
Ghani & Tirmizi, 1991
) and Weizhou Island, Gungxi, China (
Jiang et al. 2007
). The present study newly records this species from central Philippines .
